    "description": "Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Credit Analyst for our Ahmedabad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates:\nAxis Bank Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in VBA\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates!",
